description: Bavaria German Restaurant invites you to experience authentic German cuisine expertly prepared and served by our warm, friendly staff since 1997. A true restaurant treasure of Iloilo City! Our dining room is casual-elegant and so conveniently close to the Jaro Cathedral and the Jaro Plaza. Please explore our extensive menu, enjoy different kinds of imported German beers, eat at our dining room with cozy spots to dine with friends and family. You can also check out our beautiful German decorations and our many wall art paintings inspired by the province of Bavaria. Know more about us here on Facebook by exploring our hundreds of photos and even like our page for updates. We are so proud to be a part of Iloilo for 20 years and want to extend our thanks and warm wishes to all of our treasured guests!!!

name: Bourbon Street Grill and Bar
location_string: Iloilo City, Iloilo Province, Panay Island, Visayas

photo.caption: Specialty of the House Babyback ribs

description: BOURBON STREET: A PLACE FOR FAVORITESAdmit it, you have your favorites, even a favorite child or parent. You always have your favorite movie, song, shoes, and even a favorite sleepwear.Everyone’s favorite ribs in Iloilo is at Bourbon Street. Those luscious ribs are even hand carried and air flown to various destinations. To some, Bourbon Street means pizza, specifically a 9-inch thin crust pizza in a shape of a perfect square. And to some, it is the Southwest Salad, Fish and Chips, or the “well-crafted” US Angus Ribeye. The place even serves a huge burger, ground within the premises using only US Beef cuts meant for steaks, served on its own custom-made stainless steel plate.After dinner, Bourbon Street is a favorite place for drinks and some fun with friends. Be it totally ice-cold beer, or a very stiff cocktail, nothing beats chilling in any of its three rooms or its upper-floor balcony with your favorite DJ playing.A favorite place Bourbon Street truly is to its loyal guests. From those fresh out of the office drones thirsty for a drop of beer or to 2:00 A.M. clubbers on a Saturday night crawl, the place surprisingly please everyone. And in between, there is the dining crowd. People come back to Bourbon Street week after week after week, there to enjoy their favorites. What is your favorite at Bourbon Street? Is it one, two, or many?

description: At Straight Up, the evolving cityscape comprises the main attraction, together with cool cocktails, great music and fashionable interiors. The panoramic view covers East to West, from the Atria park amid fashionable boutiques and restaurants of Shops at Atria. Straight Up offers guests a choice of lounging indoors or enjoying the cool evening breeze “al fresco”. Cold, seafood and “carne” tapas are menu highlights - exquisite in taste and presentation, supplemented by a range dinner items, desserts, and others in-between. During “apericena” (pre-dinner cocktails), guests enjoy a complimentary buffet of canapes with any order of alcoholic beverage from 6:00 to 8:00 pm daily. Audal entertainment is a mix of 21st century lounge interspersed with guest acoustic band on Fridays and dj's on Saturdays.
